OL,3,CHas your airport raised the price of
OL,4,C'kiss-and-fly' drop-off parking fees
OL,6,FMore than half of the UK's 20 busiest
OL,7,Fairports have raised the price of
OL,8,Fshort drop-off parking near their
OL,9,Fterminals, according to research by
OL,10,Fthe RAC.
OL,12,FLondon Gatwick, Stansted, Bristol,
OL,13,FLeeds Bradford and Southampton now all
OL,14,Fcharge the top rate of #7 for short-
OL,15,Fterm "kiss-and-fly" parking.
OL,17,FIn contrast, nine of the busiest 10
OL,18,Fairports in the EU charge nothing to
OL,19,Fdrop off passengers.
