OL,3,CHas your airport raised the price of
OL,4,C'kiss-and-fly' drop-off parking fees
OL,6,FGeorge Best Belfast City Airport had
OL,7,Fthe biggest percentage rise increasing
OL,8,Ftheir rates by 33% to a total of #4.
OL,10,FThis was followed by Newcastle Airport
OL,11,Fwho increased their drop-off parking
OL,12,Fby 25% to #5, and London Heathrow,
OL,13,FEdinburgh, Birmingham and Liverpool
OL,14,Fwho all upped their drop-off fees by
OL,15,F20% to #6.
OL,17,FCardiff Airport has also introduced a
OL,18,Fdrop-off fee for the first time,
OL,19,Fstarting at #3.
