OL,3,CHas your airport raised the price of
OL,4,C'kiss-and-fly' drop-off parking fees
OL,6,FHowever, on a cost-per-minute basis,
OL,7,Fthe most expensive airports are London
OL,8,FLuton and Manchester, where drivers
OL,9,Fhave to fork out #5 to stop for just
OL,10,Ffive minutes.
OL,12,FThe RAC's senior policy officer Rod
OL,13,FDennis said "the sky really does seem
OL,14,Fto be the limit" when it came to these
OL,15,Fcharges.
OL,17,FHe added: "The main reason drivers
OL,18,Fdrop off at airports, according to our
OL,19,Fresearch, is to help people with bulky
OL,20,Fand often heavy luggage."
